Schema Definitions

RCMD-SHOW-IPFRR-EVENT-INFO:

IP-Frr Run information

trigger-time: string

Trigger time (eg: Apr 24 13:16:04.961)

remote-node: RCMD-SHOW-IPFRR-RLFA-PQ-NODE

Remote Node Information

event-id-xr: integer

IP-Frr Event ID

completed-spf-run: integer

IP-Frr Completed reference SPF Run Number

ipfrr-statistic: RCMD-SHOW-IPFRR-STATS

IP-Frr Statistics categorized by priority

wait-time: integer

Waiting Time (in milliseconds)

total-routes: integer

Cumulative Number of Routes for all priorities

coverage: string

Coverage in percentage for all priorities

duration: string

Duration for the calculation (in milliseconds)

trigger-spf-run: integer

IP-Frr Triggered reference SPF Run Number

partially-protected-routes: integer

Cumulative Number of Partially Protected Routes

fully-protected-routes: integer

Cumulative Number of Fully Protected Routes

start-time-offset: string

Start Time offset from trigger time (in milliseconds)

Example
{
  "trigger-time": "string",
  "remote-node": [
    {
      "path-count": "integer",
      "primary-path": [
        {
          "interface-name": "string",
          "neighbour-address": "string"
        }
      ],
      "remote-node-id": "string",
      "interface-name": "string",
      "in-use-time": "string",
      "neighbour-address": "string"
    }
  ],
  "event-id-xr": "integer",
  "completed-spf-run": "integer",
  "ipfrr-statistic": [
    {
      "local-lfa-coverage": "string",
      "remote-lfa-coverage": "string",
      "priority": "string",
      "total-routes": "integer",
      "coverage": "string",
      "below-threshold": "boolean",
      "partially-protected-routes": "integer",
      "fully-protected-routes": "integer"
    }
  ],
  "wait-time": "integer",
  "total-routes": "integer",
  "coverage": "string",
  "duration": "string",
  "trigger-spf-run": "integer",
  "partially-protected-routes": "integer",
  "fully-protected-routes": "integer",
  "start-time-offset": "string"
}

RCMD-IAEXT-PRIORITY-SUMMARY:

Priority Summary for Inter-area & external calculation

threshold-exceeded: boolean

Threshold exceeded

type4ls-as: integer

Number of Type 4 LSA

level: string critical, high, medium, low

Critical, High, Medium or Low

ip-convergence-time: RCMD-TIMESTAMP

Convergence time for IP route programming

mpls-convergence-time: RCMD-TIMESTAMP

Convergence time for MPLS label programming

type57ls-as: integer

Number of Type 5/7 LSA

route-statistics: RCMD-STAT

Route statistics

type3ls-as: integer

Number of Type 3 LSA

Example
{
  "threshold-exceeded": "boolean",
  "type4ls-as": "integer",
  "level": "string",
  "ip-convergence-time": {
    "fastest-node-name": "string",
    "minimum-time": "string",
    "slowest-node-name": "string",
    "maximum-time": "string"
  },
  "mpls-convergence-time": {
    "fastest-node-name": "string",
    "minimum-time": "string",
    "slowest-node-name": "string",
    "maximum-time": "string"
  },
  "type57ls-as": "integer",
  "route-statistics": {
    "touches": "integer",
    "adds": "integer",
    "unreachables": "integer",
    "reachables": "integer",
    "modifies": "integer",
    "deletes": "integer"
  },
  "type3ls-as": "integer"
}

RCMD-SHOW-PREFIX-PATH:

Prefix Path information

lfa-path: RCMD-SHOW-IPFRR-LFA-PATH

Backup Path Informatoin

path-metric: integer

Path Metric

interface-name: string

Interface Name

change-type: string none, add, delete, modify, no-change

Event Add/Delete

neighbour-address: string

Nexthop Address

Example
{
  "lfa-path": [
    {
      "remote-node-id": "string",
      "lfa-type": "string",
      "change-type": "string",
      "interface-name": "string",
      "neighbour-address": "string",
      "path-metric": "integer"
    }
  ],
  "path-metric": "integer",
  "interface-name": "string",
  "change-type": "string",
  "neighbour-address": "string"
}

RCMD-SHOW-STRING-MEMORY-INFO:

string memory Information

failure: integer

Cache-hit failure

total: integer

Total request

success: integer

Cache-hit success

size: integer

Size of the block

Example
{
  "failure": "integer",
  "total": "integer",
  "success": "integer",
  "size": "integer"
}

RCMD-SHOW-IPFRR-PATH:

IP-Frr Remote Node Primary Path information

interface-name: string

Interface Name

neighbour-address: string

Nexthop Address

Example
{
  "interface-name": "string",
  "neighbour-address": "string"
}

RCMD-ISIS-SPF-RUN-SUMMARY:

SPF summary information

trigger-time: string

Trigger time (in hh:mm:ss.msec)

threshold-exceeded: boolean

Threshold exceeded

isis-level: string l1, l2

ISIS Level

total-lsp-changes: integer

Total number of LSP changes processed

state: string complete, in-complete, collecting, no-route-change

SPF state

priority-summary: RCMD-PRIORITY-SUMMARY

Convergence information summary on per-priority basis

is-data-complete: boolean

Whether the event has all information

duration: string

Duration of SPF calculation (in ss.msec)

type: string full, incremental, next-hop, partial-route

Type of SPF

topology: integer

Topology index (multi-topology)

Example
{
  "trigger-time": "string",
  "threshold-exceeded": "boolean",
  "isis-level": "string",
  "total-lsp-changes": "integer",
  "state": "string",
  "priority-summary": [
    {
      "threshold-exceeded": "boolean",
      "level": "string",
      "ip-convergence-time": {
        "fastest-node-name": "string",
        "minimum-time": "string",
        "slowest-node-name": "string",
        "maximum-time": "string"
      },
      "mpls-convergence-time": {
        "fastest-node-name": "string",
        "minimum-time": "string",
        "slowest-node-name": "string",
        "maximum-time": "string"
      },
      "frr-statistic": [
        {
          "total-routes": "integer",
          "partially-protected-routes": "integer",
          "coverage": "string",
          "fully-protected-routes": "integer"
        }
      ],
      "route-statistics": {
        "touches": "integer",
        "adds": "integer",
        "unreachables": "integer",
        "reachables": "integer",
        "modifies": "integer",
        "deletes": "integer"
      }
    }
  ],
  "is-data-complete": "boolean",
  "duration": "string",
  "type": "string",
  "topology": "integer"
}

RCMD-TIME:

The timestamps for each module

duration: string

Duration of processing (in ss.msec)

end-time: string

Last route process time relative to event trigger time (in ss.msec)

start-time: string

First route process time relative to event trigger time (in ss.msec)

Example
{
  "duration": "string",
  "end-time": "string",
  "start-time": "string"
}

RCMD-REGEN-LSP-INFO:

Regenerated LSP information

sequence-number: integer

Sequence Number

isis-level: string l1, l2

ISIS Level

spf-run-number: integer

SPF Run Number

reception-time: string

Reception Time on router (in hh:mm:ss.msec)

reason: string

Trigger reasons for LSP regeneration. Example: pr^ - periodic, cr^ - clear (Check the documentation for the entire list)

serial-number-xr: integer

Serial Number of the session event

lsp-id: string

LSP ID

Example
{
  "sequence-number": "integer",
  "isis-level": "string",
  "spf-run-number": "integer",
  "reception-time": "string",
  "reason": "string",
  "serial-number-xr": "integer",
  "lsp-id": "string"
}

RCMD-LSP-INFO:

LSP information

sequence-number: integer

Sequence Number

reception-time: string

Reception Time on router (in hh:mm:ss.msec)

change-type: string new, delete, modify, noop

Add, Delete, Modify

lsp-id: string

LSP ID

Example
{
  "sequence-number": "integer",
  "reception-time": "string",
  "change-type": "string",
  "lsp-id": "string"
}

RCMD-SHOW-PREFIX-INFO:

prefix statistics information

threshold-exceed-count: integer

No. of times threshold got exceeded

last-event-time: string

Last event trigger time

prefix-lenth: integer

Prefix length

low-priority: integer

No. of times processed under Low Priority

add-count: integer

No. of times route gets Added

last-change-type: string none, add, delete, modify, no-change

Last event Add/Delete

medium-priority: integer

No. of times processed under Medium Priority

prefix: string

Prefix

last-cost: integer

Last Known Cost

high-priority: integer

No. of times processed under High Priority

critical-priority: integer

No. of times processed under Critical Priority

last-route-type: string ospf, intra, inter, ext-1, ext-2, nssa-1, nssa-2, isis, l1-summary, l1, l2-summary, l2, inter-area-summary, inter-area, default-attached

Last event Route Type

last-priority: string critical, high, medium, low

Last event processed priority

modify-count: integer

No. of times route gets Deleted

delete-count: integer

No. of times route gets Deleted

Example
{
  "threshold-exceed-count": "integer",
  "last-event-time": "string",
  "prefix-lenth": "integer",
  "low-priority": "integer",
  "add-count": "integer",
  "last-change-type": "string",
  "medium-priority": "integer",
  "prefix": "string",
  "last-cost": "integer",
  "high-priority": "integer",
  "critical-priority": "integer",
  "last-route-type": "string",
  "last-priority": "string",
  "modify-count": "integer",
  "delete-count": "integer"
}

RCMD-OSPF-SPF-RUN-SUMMARY:

SPF summary information

trigger-time: string

Trigger time (in hh:mm:ss.msec)

threshold-exceeded: boolean

Threshold exceeded

start-time: string

Start time (offset from event trigger time in ss .msec)

total-type357lsa-changes: integer

Total number of Type 3/5/7 LSA changes processed

total-inter-area-and-external-batches: integer

Total number of inter-area/external computation batches

state: string complete, in-complete, collecting, no-route-change

SPF state

priority-summary: RCMD-PRIORITY-SUMMARY

Convergence information summary on per-priority basis

is-data-complete: boolean

Whether the event has all information

duration: string

Duration of complete SPF calculation (in ss .msec)

total-dijkstra-runs: integer

Total number of Dijkstra runs

total-type12lsa-changes: integer

Total number of Type 1/2 LSA changes processed

Session State

Remote Node ID

Protected Route Count

route-count: integer

Total Route Count

lsr-id: string

Label Space Router ID

remote-label-count: integer

Remote Label Count

transport-address: string

Transport Address

in-use-time: string

Inuse time of the Session

path-count: integer

Total Path Count
